data.description: Welcome to the residence you've been anticipating all year. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by a tastefully decorated living space ideal for post-work relaxation. Further inside, you'll discover a generously sized dining room equipped with a modern coffee bar, seamlessly connected to a spacious and well-appointed kitchen. Each bedroom in this home surpasses standard sizes and features large walk-in closets. Recent improvements include a fresh coat of paint throughout, a new garage motor, a state-of-the-art AC unit, and contemporary lighting fixtures. Secure your viewing appointment today, and ensure your in time for the approaching holiday season.
